        "text": "Deuteronomy 4:41-43",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—raises questions at the heart of the problem of the structure of the book of Deuteronomy. Does it signify that once the book began here and consisted only of the discourses 5–11 and the laws 12–26; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
